{"type": "article", "id": 5414, "title": "Whistle 吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-21T07:27:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233845pzGJS65QjBnfRb2H.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这款名为「Whistle」的吊灯出自捷克女设计师 Lucie Koldova 之手，是她为拥有百年历史的捷克灯饰制造商 BROKIS 设计的一款产品，将亮相本周开幕的巴黎家具装饰展览会。其设计灵感来源于传统喇叭的轮廓，Lucie Koldova 选用了人工吹制而成的透明玻璃作为灯罩，并给灯罩内部施以彩色胶印油墨，使得每一款不同色彩的灯具散射出不一样的光芒。要知道 BROKIS 就是从玻璃工坊起家的，所以这款喇叭吊顶也可以一窥 BROKIS 对于材料的掌控力。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233842cvTMuqf40W5ptARe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.084375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052338438JHudhvkE9jmsWzP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233844l6B42gIxU3CJ0LsQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233844wWEqT0Pszi2St9dB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}